		<section>
					<h2>Optimize middleware software performance to minimize risk and meet service levels</h2>
										<p>Middleware technologies are the cornerstone for integrating disparate systems. The danger of having a complex middleware layer is that small problems might not come to your attention before they turn into big ones. What&rsquo;s more, viewing individual environments without an enterprise-wide view leads to increased costs, wasted skills, and lost time.</p>
							</section>











    	    










							        											
		        	    		
		<section>
					<h2>What to look for in middleware software management solutions</h2>
										<ul>
<li>Real-time monitoring of middleware product performance</li>
<li>Enterprise-wide view across application components</li>
<li>End-to-end middleware transaction tracing</li>
<li>Early problem detection to accelerate MTTR</li>
<li>Data gathering, analysis, and reporting</li>
<li>Secure, auditable configuration management</li>
</ul>
							</section>











    	    










							        											
		        	    		
		<section>
					<h2>Master complexity in your middleware technology layer</h2>
										BMC TrueSight Middleware Management eliminates the risk of missing a problem in a complex middleware layer. Real-time monitoring combined with proactive notifications help you stay on top of potential problems. Transaction tracing allows you to rapidly identify exactly where a problem got its start. <br /> 
<ul>
<li>Get a real-time view of your entire middleware product environment and its performance.</li>
<li>Manage multiple middleware products securely and remotely, from a central interface.</li>
<li>Receive detailed notifications whenever your middleware software is negatively affecting business operations.</li>
<li>Automatically correct common issues, taking the burden off of your IT staff.</li>
<li>Perform common tasks on middleware objects without any platform-specific skills.</li>
</ul>
