    						<a href="/it-solutions/application-performance-management.html"  target="_self" >Application Performance Management</a>
    					</dt>
    					    						<dd>
    							BMC application performance management (APM) solutions deliver deep insight for better, faster decision-making, reduced manual effort for IT staff, and more satisfied business users.
    						</dd>
    																		</dl>
			</article>
			</section>





       	    










